          <div class="card-description">
            <p class="muted">When purchasing an art object, you want to know it is the real deal. A certificate helps art collectors, proving it's the original. Often this is done through certification, yet these can be forged as well.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column card uc">
        <div class="card-content bc">
          <h3 class="accent-text">Counterfeiting certificates</h3>
          <div class="card-description">
            <p class="muted">Paper-based certificates are easy to counterfeit. Backdating a purchase or changing the unique identifier of an art object is a piece of cake with today's software tools.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="column card uc">
        <div class="card-content bc">
          <h3 class="accent-text">Validation of the certificate</h3>
          <div class="card-description">
